content.data: This time we will create a wood Counter Top from a base object. It will have a total of four parts. See the drawings below.

Before creating the wood Counter Top we will need to go to the PartManager and add a couple of new parts to CABINET VISION. We will add a part called "WT" for the "Wood Top" and we will add a part called "SK" for the "Skirting" to go around the top.
We will also need to go into our cabinet part Material Schedules and pick materials to make these parts out of.
